item.description: Orama Plug and play React charts. Responsive layout Automatic data type extraction Freely composable marks Canvas rendering and caching optimizations Configurable theme Orama has been powering Kensho’s charts in production for more than a year. /horáō, “to see, spiritually and mentally” – a vision, focusing on the impact it has on the one beholding the vision. Quick Start $ npm install orama Get an array of objects: [{key1, key2}, {key1, key2}, .
